org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl

Class LevelMonitorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.ItemFeatureEntryImpl
        • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.LevelMonitorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ItemFeatureEntry, LevelMonitor

    public class LevelMonitorImpl
extends ItemFeatureEntryImpl
implements LevelMonitor
    An implementation of the model object 'Level Monitor'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Preset
    • Cap
    • Severity
    • Lower Ok
    • Included Ok
    • Prefix
    • Demote Prefix
    • Suppress Events
    • Require Ack
    • Monitor Type
